            <div class="p-7 flex-grow flex flex-col gap-5">
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Lead our premium outstation and tour packages. Navigate scenic routes across states while ensuring passenger safety and comfort over multi-day trips.</p>
              <div class="space-y-4 flex-grow">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-[#1E2D5A] mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-slate-100 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Requirements</h4>
